Disclaimer

GuardScope is a defensive platform. It does not perform unauthorized network
probing, brute-forcing, exploitation, persistence, stealth scanning, or
auto-submission of vulnerability reports. The optional ``offensive/``
sub-package wraps external security tools (Nmap, Hydra, sqlmap, Nuclei) and
constrains their execution to explicitly registered loopback-only lab
targets via a hard scope guard (loopback check + lab whitelist + rate limit
+ audit log). Public, third-party, or production targets are refused at
the API boundary.

See ``LEGAL.md`` for the complete safety boundary. By using this software
you agree to operate it only on systems you own or are explicitly
authorized to test.
